name: created
description: Specifies the entity responsible for originating or producing something.

name: developed
description: Indicates that an entity was responsible for the creation or improvement of something.

name: partnered with
description: Reflects collaboration or alliance between two entities.

name: purchased
description: Denotes acquisition of something by one entity through payment.

name: received
description: Indicates that an entity accepted or was given something by another.

name: invested in
description: Indicates financial or resource commitment by one entity to another.

name: verified
description: Represents that an entity confirmed the accuracy or truth of another.

name: interacted with
description: Shows engagement or communication between entities.

name: manages
description: Reflects the act of overseeing or directing an entity or operation.

name: advises
description: Suggests that one entity provides guidance or recommendations to another.

name: rated
description: Represents a judgment or evaluation made by one entity about another.

name: recommends
description: Suggests endorsement or approval of one entity by another.

name: authored
description: Represents that an entity is the creator or writer of a work.

name: belongs to
description: Suggests membership or inclusion within a larger group or category.

name: governs
description: Indicates that one entity directs or controls another.

name: trusts
description: Reflects confidence or reliance on another entity’s integrity or actions.

name: follows
description: Represents that one entity follows the updates or actions of another.

name: supports
description: Expresses endorsement, aid, or backing of an entity by another.

name: contributed to
description: Indicates participation or input into a project or outcome.

name: verified
description: Denotes that an entity has been authenticated or validated by another.

name: controls
description: Suggests authority or influence over an entity.

name: owns
description: Represents ownership or possession of an entity by another.

name: invested in
description: Indicates financial or resource commitment by one entity to another, with the expectation of future returns or benefits.

name: sold
description: Represents the transaction in which one entity transferred ownership of something to another in exchange for payment or consideration.

name: is responsible for
description: Reflects accountability or duty for a task or outcome.

name: cited
description: Indicates that one entity referenced or mentioned another in support.

name: is based on
description: Denotes that something derives its foundation from another entity.

name: uses
description: Indicates utilization or employment of one entity by another.

name: backed by
description: Denotes financial or moral support provided by another entity.

name: participated in
description: Indicates involvement or engagement in an event or activity.

name: has expertise in
description: Specifies an entity’s proficiency or knowledge in a certain area.

name: collaborates on
description: Denotes joint effort by entities toward a shared project or goal.

name: oversees
description: Denotes supervision or management of an entity by another.

name: reviews
description: Reflects evaluation or critique of an entity’s work or performance.

name: analyzed
description: Represents examination or detailed study of an entity by another.

name: researched
description: Denotes systematic investigation conducted by one entity on another.

name: completed
description: Indicates the fulfillment or conclusion of a task or process.

name: mentored
description: Represents guidance or advice provided by one entity to another.

name: teaches
description: Reflects the act of imparting knowledge or instruction to another entity.

name: is located in
description: Specifies the geographic or digital location of an entity.

name: issued
description: Represents that an entity has formally provided or distributed something.

name: is influenced by
description: Shows that one entity’s behavior or state has been affected by another.

name: collaborates with
description: Denotes active cooperation or joint effort between entities.

name: discussed
description: Indicates that one entity conversed or deliberated with another on a subject.

name: contributed data to
description: Denotes that an entity provided data or information to a system.

name: is part of
description: Indicates that one entity is a component or subset of another.

name: is associated with
description: Establishes a general connection between two entities.

name: is connected to
description: Indicates a direct relationship or link between two entities.

name: engaged with
description: Shows involvement or interaction between entities.

name: shares
description: Indicates that one entity distributes or communicates something with others.

name: holds a stake in
description: Indicates financial or vested interest in an entity by another.

name: has a relationship with
description: Indicates a defined connection or interaction between entities.
